query:
SELECT 
  p.productId,
  p.name,
  p.brand,
  p.productType,
  p.phaseType
FROM products p
LEFT JOIN product_categories pc ON p.id = pc.productId
WHERE pc.productId IS NULL
ORDER BY p.productType, p.brand
LIMIT 80;
